	<section class="section fade-in">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>Our Hardware Implementation Process</h2>
			<div class="grid grid-3">
				<div class="feature process-step">
					<h3>Assess & Specify</h3>
					<p>We perform an OPSEC Health Check to determine if certified hardware is the right solution for your specific data protection needs.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="feature process-step">
					<h3>Source & Configure</h3>
					<p>We procure through authorized channels and pre-configure devices with your security policies before deployment.</p>
